{"tid":227611,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"譚仔呀姨有一個秘密嘅身份","createTime":"2017-05-03T10:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T18:36:12.000Z","uid":41814,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4fde424d9fb413193a196a3916ed6d14c080adc3","tid":227611,"uid":41814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:03:00.000Z","msg":"呢班平平無奇 看似係一班弱質女流嘅呀姨<br />\n講住一口流利嘅大陸腔廣東話<br />\n其實係偉大祖國派落黎嘅間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每當佢地飯聚嘅時候就係進行緊戰略會議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而禁多間分店就係佢地嘅軍火庫同哨站<br />\n<br />\n仲有嘅係 佢地係碗譚仔度會落一種令人上癮嘅化學物質 賺到盈利嘅同時 又可以控制到人對食物選擇嘅需求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n祖國實在係太冇機心 太偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65fa93c0768120be67693a2e5430ddbbc793bb6","tid":227611,"uid":88178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e95f9c777e27ea55af2ec35a5e0674027d7fc3c","tid":227611,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:24:42.000Z","msg":"有冇理據啊？<br />\n冇就del你post啦"},{"pid":"4345c82ebea60271134a458a5c5f48aa7698c659","tid":227611,"uid":49055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:25:00.000Z","msg":"依俾凍撚死"},{"pid":"e998c6c7888bd4e32841cc27b1cb1c6500aedcd1","tid":227611,"uid":41814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:58:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇理據啊？<br />\n冇就del你post啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咪充足理據囉"},{"pid":"a3c7ce4ea868a69837cbc96e7a0f69a58db61a68","tid":227611,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:59:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇理據啊？<br />\n冇就del你post啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咪充足理據囉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},